edu.common.dynamicextensions.domain
Class DomainObjectFactory

java.lang.Object
  edu.common.dynamicextensions.domain.DomainObjectFactory
public class DomainObjectFactory
extends java.lang.Object

This is a singleton class which provides methods for generating domain objects. For each domain object a create method is provided.
